    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is ideal for someone looking for a project or a source for parts. The exterior has significant rust issues, particularly around the rocker panels, and the paint is peeling in several areas. Mechanically, the engine requires a major overhaul and the transmission is slipping, so it will likely need to be towed. The interior is heavily worn with multiple tears in the upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. Sold strictly as-is.",
