    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Unlock the potential of this classic project car! Perfect for a dedicated hobbyist or anyone looking for a rewarding restoration journey, this vehicle is ready for some serious TLC to bring it back to its former glory. It's a fantastic opportunity to roll up your sleeves and create something truly special from a solid foundation!",
