    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of unparalleled distinction. This specimen remains in showroom condition, exhibiting an unblemished aesthetic and mechanical integrity that satisfies the most discerning collector. Meticulously maintained and preserved, it represents the pinnacle of its class. We invite you to experience a standard of excellence rarely encountered in the pre-owned market.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so excited to show you my pride and joy. This car is in absolutely stunning condition\u2014it basically looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I have babied this beauty since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it stays spotless. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for something that's practically brand new, you've found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a peerless example featuring the iconic 2JZ-GTE twin-turbocharged inline-six, paired with the robust Getrag V160 6-speed manual gearbox. This vehicle retains its factory-correct sequential forced induction system, exhibiting perfect compression across all cylinders and zero shaft play in the turbines. The drivetrain is anchored by a factory Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque vectoring. The chassis is laser-straight, with all original spot welds intact and a pristine undercarriage free of oxidation. Suspension kinematics remain sharp thanks to fresh OEM bushings and a perfectly dialed double-wishbone configuration. The interior is a time capsule, featuring flawless upholstery with no bolster deformation and fully functional analog instrumentation. This is a turnkey, collector-grade specimen for the technical purist.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "2021 model. Mint condition. Single owner. Zero accidents. Garage kept. No mechanical issues. Full service history included.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that redefines the standard for a pre-owned vehicle. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, shielded from the elements since its first mile. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory-fresh luster, completely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings; it has been recently treated with a professional-grade ceramic coating to ensure its mirror-like finish remains protected. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule. The premium leather upholstery remains supple and uncreased, with no wear on the bolsters and absolutely no fading on the dashboard or trim. Every electronic feature, from the infotainment system to the seat heaters, operates with factory precision. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach. It features a comprehensive service history with all maintenance performed exclusively by brand-certified technicians using genuine parts. The engine bay is spotless, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road salt or oxidation. Included with the sale are the original window sticker, all service receipts, two sets of keys, and the unused factory floor mats. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did on the showroom floor.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are proud to present this impeccably preserved specimen, a vehicle that transcends the standard used market. This unit remains in showroom condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original integrity. Meticulously maintained and strictly inspected, this car represents an exceptional opportunity for the collector or driver who demands nothing less than perfection. Secure a vehicle that mirrors the quality of a new acquisition with the character of a modern classic.",
      "price": 47800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    }
